- First activity (extended of abstract BaseAuthenticationActivity) launches with the correct account.
- Start new activity (extended of abstract AppCompatActivity)
- OnCreate called in new activity.
- Firebase fires onAuthenticationChange.
- Causes the authentication handler to fire and get user, setting up header
- Header setup calls setProfiles. 
- setProfile calls switchProfiles thinks that mCurrentProfile is the incorrect account. The response of the switchable accounts is ordered by the JavaEE response from my server response in SQL.
