vistaco:
so, i solved the problem.
for anybody who have a same problem.
in CrossfadeDrawerLayout put this method and call it when you want.
if you have better idea , tell me :)
```
public void openDrawer() {
        mDrawerOpened = true;
        mIsCrossfaded = true;
        mSmallView.setAlpha(0);
        mSmallView.setClickable(false);
        mLargeView.bringToFront();
        mLargeView.setAlpha(1);
        mLargeView.setClickable(true);
        mLargeView.setVisibility(View.VISIBLE);
        mContainer.getLayoutParams().width = mMaxWidth;
        mContainer.requestLayout();
    new Handler().postDelayed(new Runnable() {
        @Override
        public void run() {
            openDrawer(Gravity.RIGHT);
        }
    },50);
}

```.
